<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="hearts" id="hearts"></div>
    <h1>Tania, will you be my Valentine? üíò</h1>
    <p>From Saif ‚Äî I promise lots of love, laughs, and unforgettable moments.</p>
    <div class="buttons">
      <button id="yes">Yes üíï</button>
      <button id="no">No üôà</button>
      <div id="tease" style="position:absolute;font-size:14px;color:#7b2cbf;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);padding:4px 10px;border-radius:12px;white-space:nowrap;pointer-events:none;z-index:1;"></div>
