    <div class="message" id="message">
      Tania ‚ù§Ô∏è<br><br>
      Thank you for choosing me.<br>
      I promise to love you in the calm days and hold you closer in the hard ones.
      Every smile of yours feels like home to me.
      Today, tomorrow, and always ‚Äî it‚Äôs you.
      <br><br>
      Love,<br>Saif
